## Script chiudi / PUSH (step 8)

`jiraCORE.close.story.mjs` — **solo step 8 PUSH**, non step 7:

```bash
node admin.portal.JiraCORE/jiraCORE.close.story.mjs --key {KEY}
node admin.portal.JiraCORE/jiraCORE.close.story.mjs --key {KEY} --dry-run
```

- Key: `{JIRA_KEY}-xxx` coerente con progetto istanziato
- Pillar matrix: `--pillar` (opt-in)
- Ordine interno: **catalogo** (commit) → **push branch** → **PR**; invocato da step 8 **dopo** sync Jira da WIP

