## Jira — invocazione

| Fase workflow | Jira / DB |
| --- | --- |
| Step 3 veve db | `jira_issue` read · `jira_issue_wip` write |
| Step 0 piano | `jira_issue_wip` read |
| Ok chiudi subtask | `jira_issue_wip` update subtask |
| **Step 7 chiudi** | **`jira_issue_wip` update parent** — no Atlassian · no PR |
| **Step 8 PUSH** | **Atlassian** sync + **`jira_issue`** sync da WIP + `close-story.mjs` (PR); WIP resta |
| **Step 9 PR merge** | **`jira_issue`** sync finale · **delete `jira_issue_wip`** (purge) |

| Fase | Invocazione |
| --- | --- |
| Step 0–7 | Solo DB WIP — nessun Jira Auto / MCP |
| Step 8 PUSH | WIP → Atlassian REST + WIP → `jira_issue` + `close-story.mjs` |
| Step 9 PR poll | `jiraCORE.wip.pr.poll.mjs` — gh PR state → cache → purge WIP |

